The reporter learned from the Ministry of Finance on the 30th that the four departments of the Ministry of Finance, the State Administration of Taxation, the National Development and Reform Commission and the Ministry of Commerce recently issued a joint notice to further encourage foreign investors to invest in China, the profits allocated by foreign investors from China's resident enterprises, and the scope of application of the policy of induction income tax for domestic direct investment, and the scope of application of the policy of non-inhibited foreign investment has been expanded from foreign investment to all projects and areas that are not prohibited from foreign investment.
This policy has been in force since January 1, 2018.
The notice makes it clear that the direct investment of foreign investors in the distribution of profits, including equity investment such as capital increase, new construction, and equity acquisition by foreign investors in the interest of capital increase, new construction, and equity acquisition, etc., excluding new, additions, and acquisitions of shares of listed companies in addition to eligible strategic investments.
If an overseas investor can enjoy the temporary withdrawal of the income tax policy but not actually enjoying it, he may apply for the recovery of the policy within three years from the date of actual payment of the relevant tax and refund the taxes paid.
Not only that, foreign investors enjoy the provisions of the temporary withdrawal of income tax policy treatment, the reorganization of the investment enterprise meets the special reorganization conditions, and in accordance with the special reorganization of the tax treatment, can continue to enjoy the temporary suspension of the withdrawal of income tax policy treatment.
In order to ensure that the profits shared by foreign investors are actually used for direct investment, the notice stipulates that the profits used by foreign investors for direct investment are paid in cash, and the relevant funds are transferred directly from the account of the profit distribution enterprise or equity transferor to the account of the invested enterprise or equity transferor, and the profits of foreign investors may not be transferred to other accounts at home and abroad before the direct investment; the profits used by foreign investors for direct investment are paid in non-cash forms such as physical and securities, and the relevant asset ownership directly transferred to the enterprise or the equity transferor before the direct investment shall be held or held temporarily.
The notice also requires the tax department to strengthen follow-up management in accordance with the law.
Foreign investors have enjoyed the temporary collection of induction of income tax policy, after the follow-up management of the tax department to verify that do not meet the prescribed conditions, in addition to the liability of the profit distribution enterprise, deemed that foreign investors did not declare the payment of corporate income tax in accordance with the provisions, will be investigated according to law for delaying tax liability, tax delay payment period from the date of payment of related profits.
