After the approval of Premier Li Keqiang, the State Council recently issued the Decision on Further Reducing the Catalogue of Production Permits for Industrial Products and Simplifying the Approval Procedure.
The "Decision" proposes to further reduce the catalogue of industrial product production license management, cancel the production license management of 14 industrial products, and decentralize the management authority of the production license of 4 industrial products to the quality and technical supervision department of the provincial people's governments.
After this reform, the implementation of industrial product production license management of products will be reduced from 38 to the current 24 categories last year.
The "Decision" is clear, the implementation of simplified approval procedures for products in the catalogue.
The first is to change the pre-issence product inspection of the issuing authority organization to the product inspection and qualification report issued by the enterprise submitted by the qualified inspection and testing institution at the time of application.
Second, in addition to hazardous chemicals, the provincial people's government quality and technical supervision department (market supervision and management department) to implement the product implementation of the site review, enterprises submit applications and product inspection qualified reports and make commitments to ensure product quality and safety, after the form of review can receive the production license, and then accept the on-site review within the prescribed time.
The third is the different types of products in the production and operation catalogue of enterprises, in accordance with the principle of "one enterprise, one certificate", when applying for a new license or applying for a new license, it is reviewed and issued a license.
The "Decision" requires that all regions and relevant departments should solidly promote the work of reducing the catalogue and simplifying the approval process.
Increase the commitment of enterprises to publicize and post-site review efforts, strengthen credit supervision and restraint means, implement the main responsibility of enterprise quality, and revoke production licenses for false promises and non-compliance.
For the cancellation of industrial product production license management products, we must effectively strengthen post-event supervision, involving public health and safety, environmental protection and other products can be converted into mandatory certification, listed positive lists and publicized to the public, unified certification standards, reasonable reduction and certification testing projects, mandatory certification costs in principle by the financial level of the burden of the system.
Take support measures to encourage enterprises to carry out voluntary certification, promote the establishment of brands and expand the market.
It is necessary to benchmark international advanced standards and promote the improvement of industrial product quality.
Give full play to the role of third-party social organizations to ensure the quality and safety of industrial products.
For the products that retain the production license management of industrial products, we must improve the standard system, give full play to the advantages of industry supervision, strengthen the responsibility of "who approves and who supervises", dynamically assess product quality and safety risks, and timely reduce the catalogue, delegate approval authority or convert to certification management.
In September, China's comprehensive PMI increased manufacturing PMI.
China's National Bureau of Statistics released data on the 30th, in September, China's comprehensive PMI output index was 54.1%, higher than the previous month and the annual average of 0.3 and 0.1 percentage points, indicating that the overall production and operation activities of Chinese enterprises remained stable.
