There is no "threshold" of the month center: quality certification promotes quality improvement.
With the pull of the "two-child economy" and the prosperity of the mother and baby market, from the north to the third and fourth tier cities, various grades have sprung up various grades of monthly clubhouses.
At present, the month of the month of the meeting to meet the consumption needs of the masses, charging from tens of thousands of yuan or even hundreds of thousands of yuan, but at the same time in an awkward situation, this institution has no threshold so far, there is still a blank area of supervision.
The State Administration of Market Supervision recently launched the 2018 "Quality Month" series of activities, and the reporter came to a five-star monthly sub-center in Tianjin to visit the maternal and child care service certification experience.
General monthly centers provide services such as newborn care, nutritious meals, and postpartum repair and shaping.
In this month's center, the reporter saw that the nurse checked the daily breastfeeding of the newborn, and the professional carer provided detailed care services such as bathing and touching for the newborn.
At the same time, in order to meet the needs of new mothers, from the early days of the month wound care, to the mid-to-late period of the mesomatic care and other services, to provide Chinese medicine treatment and beauty and other nursing projects, to help mothers to restore their posture.
