The head of the Yuezi Center said they were the only one in all five-star moon-based centers in Tianjin to receive B-class service certification.
"Although some customers do not understand the meaning of B-level certification at first, they have forced enterprises to strictly standardize process management through certification, so that customers can benefit, which is of great significance to the long-term development of enterprises," he said.
