The lawyer carries the court on the axe head?
The news was really exciting at first glance, and it also blew up the pot in the legal circle.
Fujian Quanzhou China Law then fined the lawyers involved 500 yuan and recommended in writing that the Quanzhou Municipal Bar Association should investigate and deal with it.
According to the Beijing News, a few days ago, the Quanzhou Municipal Law Association issued a formal notice that the behavior of the two lawyers does not involve violations of the law, and shall not be punished according to law.
Judging from the multi-party reports, Quanzhou Municipal Law Association's treatment is not to protect short or confrontation, but has been recognized by the Quanzhou Central Court.
An incident that could have caused tension within the legal community was eventually properly resolved.
The reversal of the matter stems from a more complete truth reduction: the lawyer involved carries the axe with the defendant's murder weapon, the same model, but not on the edge, only in the evidence link to make supporting evidence, there is no act of intimidation or "sealing the court's safety" subjective intention.
There are four very important details to determine whether the lawyer's behavior is illegal and illegal, and there are four very important details to pay attention to: First, the local court has two previous sessions, only presented an axe photo, from the point of view of defense, showing the original axe has its necessity; second, the axe was purchased only an hour before the trial, not the lawyer did not seek the judge's consent, but objectively failed to contact the judge; the whole axe was not used too much or improperly; its four, the lawyer involved publicly recognized the error for the first time, and expressed apologies to the court.
Combined with these circumstances, it can be seen that the lawyer involved "take the court in court" has nothing to do, only to defend.
After clarifying the whole facts, the Quanzhou Municipal Law Association did not push the boat with water, but took a decision not to punish the pressure.
This decision can also stand the test of facts and laws.
As for the axes that will be brought to court as a control knife without court permission, it is indeed easy to cause unease and misunderstanding.
Out of safety and caution, the Quanzhou Middle Court's previous fine penalties and judicial advice were also understandable.
In order to safeguard the dignity of lawyers and prevent individual courts from making trouble to lawyers, the Supreme Law issued the Rules for the Security Inspection of the Judicial Police of the People's Court in 2014, which establishes the principle that lawyers do not need to carry out personal safety inspections in court.
Since the release of the rule, lawyers have led by example, and there have been few incidents of security violations due to security checks.
In a very rare example of Quanzhou, as long as it is in a spirit of mutual respect and understanding, misunderstanding is not difficult to eliminate.
As a self-regulatory organization for the lawyers industry, the Bar Association undertakes the dual mission of punishing illegality and safeguarding legality.
In the past, individual legal organizations were criticized for being more focused on punishment and failing to guarantee.
The Quanzhou Law Association's decision, both in terms of process and results, is commendable, setting an example for more Correspondents to perform their duties correctly.
Which tax benefits will affect our money bags from October 1st?
Xinhua News Agency Shanghai October 1st (Reporter Sang Tong) The new personal income tax law will be implemented from November 1, 2019, in order to allow the broad masses of the people to enjoy the tax reduction dividend as soon as possible, from October 1st, the actual salary income of taxpayers will be deducted according to the starting point of 5000 yuan per month, and the new tax rate table will be applied.
With the landing of the New Deal, what are the benefits that will affect the people's money bags?
One of the benefits: the tax reduction in salary and salary is obvious
Taxpayers who obtain salary and salary after October 1st can deduct the basic deduction of 5000 yuan / month and apply the new tax rate scale, and most taxpayers have different degrees of tax cuts, especially the tax cuts for middle- and middle-income people are more obvious.
According to the tax reduction table of different income groups, after deducting the "three insurances and one gold", the monthly income of 8000 yuan, 20000 yuan, 50,000 yuan, after tax reform tax payable is 90 yuan, 290 yuan, 1590 yuan, 9090 yuan compared with the monthly starting point 3500 yuan, the corresponding tax reduction ratio is 73.9%, 61.1%, 49.0%, 18.8%.
It is worth noting that due to holiday reasons, the wages that should have been paid in accordance with the law at the end of September by law can apply the new basic deduction fees and tax scale.
To this end, the withholding client software used by the tax department has provided the corresponding tax calculation function, but the corresponding tax tax still needs to be declared during the statutory filing period.
Good two: the low tax bracket is obviously pulled up
In addition to raising the starting point, the new tax rate table will be applied from October 1st.
The seven-tier tax rate of salary and salary income is consistent with the previous, there is no change, but the tax rate level has changed significantly, 3%, 10%, 20% three-grade low tax rate range has been significantly expanded, and the tax rate range of 25% has been reduced, while the grade level of 30%, 35%, 45% of the three tranches of higher tax rates has remained unchanged.
It is worth noting that the tax law has also adjusted the tax rate of production and operation income, of which the lower limit of the highest 35% tax rate has been raised from 100,000 yuan to 50 million yuan.
This means that individual business owners and individual wholly-owned partnerships will all benefit from tax reform.
"From the perspective of the preliminary calculation of the personal tax reduction of Shanghai taxpayers, the majority of taxpayers will fully feel the dividends of individual tax reform, especially the tax reduction rate of middle- and low-income people is obvious."
Lan Min, head of the personal income tax department of the Shanghai Municipal Tax Bureau of the State Administration of Taxation, said.
Three: Tax services are more convenient and optimized
Since the publication of the new personal income tax law, the Shanghai Municipal Tax Department has carried out a series of comprehensive and extensive tax publicity actions.
On the one hand, we will carry out "one-to-one, peer-to-peer" policy counseling for key tax sources and key enterprises.
Pudong New Area Tax Bureau has visited Apple Trade (Shanghai) Co., Ltd., Alipay (China) Network Technology Co., Ltd., Red Star Meikailong Household Group Co., Ltd. and other large enterprises, the number of employees of these enterprises, the amount of money, the tax department took the initiative to guide, answer questions; Xuhui District Tax Bureau visited the large labor enterprises in the region Zhongzhi Finance Consulting Co., Ltd., Zhongzhi Shanghai Economic and Technical Cooperation Co., Ltd., etc., to collect corporate concerns, to respond to corporate concerns, to solve corporate difficulties.
On the other hand, for the general public taxpayers, the "all-round, multi-dimensional and three-dimensional" tax policy is pushed.
