After six years, Tencent welcomes major organizational structure adjustments clearly without layoffs-China New Network
On the 30th, Tencent announced the official launch of a new round of overall strategic upgrading, the organizational structure ushered in a new round of optimization and adjustment after six years, and the reorganization and integration of the original seven major business groups (BG) into six, and said that the adjustment does not involve layoffs.
Tencent's new six major business groups.
Six years later, two new business groups have appeared.
It is understood that the new business group not only maintains the advantages and characteristics of deep cultivation verticals, retains the original enterprise development business group (CDG), interactive entertainment business group (IEG), technology engineering business group (TEG), WeChat business group (WXG); but also highlights the focus on the integration effect, the new establishment of cloud and intelligent industry enterprise group (CSIG), platform and content business group (PCG).
The reporter noted that Tencent's original mobile Internet business group (MIG), the original online media business group (OMG) have all disappeared, especially OMG, and the outside world is well-known.
Tencent said that the newly established platform and content business group (PCG, that is, Platform & Content Group) will be the original social network business group (SNG), the original mobile Internet business group (MIG), the original network media business group (OMG), and the social platform, traffic platform, digital content, core technology and other highly related and highly integrated sectors, for organic split and restructuring.
The newly established Cloud and Smart Industries Group (CSIG) will integrate industry solutions such as Tencent Cloud, Internet +, Smart Retail, Education, Healthcare, Security and LBS to promote the digital upgrading of the industry.
Tencent chairman and CEO Ma Huateng said that the second half of the Internet belongs to the industrial Internet, the first half of Tencent through the connection to provide users with high-quality services, the second half of us on this basis, to help the industry and consumers to form a more open new connection ecology.
