The Embassy met with the head of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Mongolia, the General Administration of Police and the General Emergency Department for the first time to inform the relevant situation, and asked the Mongolian side to carry out search and rescue as soon as possible, and maintain close communication with the Mongolian side during the search and rescue process to ensure that the latest progress is in a timely manner.
